# Routes
# This file defines all application routes (Higher priority routes first)
# https://www.playframework.com/documentation/latest/ScalaRouting
# ~~~~

GET     /                           controllers.ApiController.index
GET     /healthcheck                controllers.ApiController.healthcheck

+ NOCSRF
POST    /check                      controllers.ApiController.check
POST    /refresh                    controllers.ApiController.refresh
POST    /rule/add                   controllers.RuleController.add
GET     /rule                       controllers.RuleController.getAll
GET     /rule/:id                   controllers.RuleController.get(id)
